                        </t:graphic>
                     </t:figure>16 Mss. photographed: <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStgm001">TGM-001</t:ref> “Four Gospels”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStgm002">TGM-002</t:ref> “Psalter”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStgm003">TGM-003</t:ref> “Loosening of the Spell”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStgm004">TGM-004</t:ref> “Book of the feast of Christs Baptism; Prayer of Insense”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStgm005">TGM-005</t:ref> “Missal”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStgm006">TGM-006</t:ref> “Missal”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStgm007">TGM-007</t:ref> “Missal”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStgm008">TGM-008</t:ref> “Vita of Arägawi”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStgm009">TGM-009</t:ref> “Book of the Absolution and other text”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStgm010">TGM-010</t:ref> “Miracles of Mary”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStgm011">TGM-011</t:ref> “Collection of Prayers”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStgm012">TGM-012</t:ref> “Horologium”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStgm013">TGM-013</t:ref> “Miracles of Jesus”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStgm014">TGM-014</t:ref> “Loosening of the spell”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStgm015">TGM-015</t:ref> “Homily of abba Jacob of Sarug”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EStgm016">TGM-016</t:ref> “Book of the Funeral Rite”.</t:ab>
      
